Interface CheckedConsumer<T, E extends Throwable>

Type Parameters:
T -
E - the exception that is thrown
Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface public interface CheckedConsumer<T, E extends Throwable>
Identical to Consumer except that the accept(Object) method may throw a checked exception.
